{
  "stem": "21582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I-- as I said, there were the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'll tell you-- please don't let me forget about Janusz Korczak, who is one example of how one Jew-- how we treated one another.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know that there are lots of people who talk about kapos, and there was a Jewish police force.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I-- I think that the Jews were often-- see, my recollections of all of that, of the kapos, with-- with the exception of a few very, very, very isolated ones-- is that they were not unkind, that-- that-- in a way, they-- they-- they were designated by or requested-- all right, the Jews in the ghetto, the Jewish community was-- was called on to form a police force.",
      "word_count": 73
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, you know, you-- you think of what the choices were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, you know, either-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think only maybe a war prisoner can understand that in order to rebel physically you-- that something has to be ripe.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But really, we did not-- at this point, there was still hope that that will pass.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, you look at your children, and you say, OK, I'll go out, and I'm going to stab a-- someone, a German, which one of my uncles did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was at the moment when his wife and daughter were shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But prior to that, you don't want to risk your child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I'd like to return to that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I must also say that maybe the one who starts the fire is responsible, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And really they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The fire was started by those who demanded them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the option for the-- for the-- for the Jewish community was-- well, first of all, we had no option.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
